Replace `http://example.com/panoramas/LaPara360.jpg` with the actual URL of your panorama image.

Note that this code assumes that the URL of the panorama image is accessible from the same domain as the HTML page. If the image is located on a different domain, you may need to add CORS headers to the server that serves the image to allow it to be loaded by the Pannellum viewer.

